quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  30,31,"Hara ko on ruttotoo…ďe e Makko; hulon Mo, √Īinnon julde nden, wata on jeye e sirkoo…ďe …ďen"
  30,32,"(wano) …ďeya senndunoo…ďe diina mun kan, …ďe woni pecce-pecce, kala fedde no weltora ko woni ka mun kon"
  30,33,"Si sa…óteende memii yim…ďe …ďen, …ďe noddira Joomi ma…ď…ďe ko …ďe ruttitii…ďe e Makko; refti si O mee…óinii …ďe yumeende immorde e Makko, e jaka fedde goo e ma…ď…ďe no kafida e Joomi mun"
  30,34,"Yo…ďe yeddu ko Men okki …ďe kon. \"Awa dakmitee, arma anndon"
  30,35,"Kaa Men jippin e ma…ď…ďe hujja (Deftere), hara honde yewta fii ko …ďe sirkaynoo kon"
  30,36,"Si Men mee…óinirii yim…ďe …ďen neema, …ďe weltoroo mo. Si bone memirii …ďe sabu ko juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen ardiniri kon, e jaka hi…ďe ta∆īoo"
  30,37,"E …ďe yi'aali wonnde Alla no ya√Ī√Īana arsike on mo O muuyani, O …ďillina? Wonii e …óum, maandeeji wonannde yim…ďe gom…óinoo…ďe"
  30,38,"Jonnu jom-…ďadiido o hakke makko on, e …ďillii…ďe e …ďii-laawol. ∆äum …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude wonande …ďeen faalaa…ďe yarluyee Alla on; ko …ďen woni maloytee…ďe …ďen. @Corrected"
  30,39,"Kala ko jonnu…óon e riba, fii on …ďeydor e jawle yim…ďe …ďen, …óum …ďeydotaako ka Alla, kala non ko okku…óon e Jakka, mo faandori…óon welayee Alla, …ďen …óon, ko sowanoytee…ďe [njo…ďdi] …ďen. @Corrected"
  30,40,"Ko Alla woni tagu…óo on, refti O arsiki on, refti O wara on, refti O wuurnita on. Hara no e kafidaa…ói mon …óin wa…óay…ói go…ó…óum e …óum? Senayeewoo-dani Mo! O toowii e kon ko …ďe sirkata"
  30,41,"Bone on fee√Īiri ka njoorndi e ka maaje, sabu ko juu…óe yim…ďe …ďen faggitii kon; fii yo O mee…óin …ďe yoga e ko …ďe huuwi; belajo'o, …ďe ruttoto"
  30,42,"Maaku: \"Yiilee ka leydi, ndaaron ko honno battane adinoo…ďe …ďen wa'unoo. Tawno ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe ko sirkoo…ďe"
  30,43,"Fewtinir yeeso maa ngon e diina focciika kan, ado √Īalaande arde immorde ka Alla nde ruttetaake. Nde √Īalnde, …ďe seeday"
  30,44,"Kala yeddu…óo, haray geddi makko …óin no fawii mo. Kala non gollu…óo mo∆ī∆īere, haray ko ko'e-ma…ď…ďe …ďe hebilani (Aljanna)"
  30,45,"fii yo O yo…ďu …ďen gom…óim…ďe …ďe golli mo∆ī∆īu…ói, e …ďural Makko ngal. Kanko On, O yi…óaa heefer…ďe …ďen"
  30,46,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko …óin: Wurtugol Mo keneeli …óin wewlinooji, e fii yo O mee…óin on e yurmeende Makko nden, e no laa…óe …óen dogira e yamiroore Makko, e fii yo o …óa…ď…ďu e …ďural Makko. Belajo'o, on yettay [Mo]"
  30,47,"Gom…óii Men nulii ado maa…óa Nulaa…ďe haa e yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, …ďe addani …ďe …ďanngannduyeeji. Men yottii e …ďen bonnu…ďe; tawi no jojji e Amen faabagol gom…óim…ďe …ďen"
  30,48,"Ko Alla woni nuloowo kenee…ói …óin, …ói sogga duule …óen; O saakitira …óum ka weeyo no O yi…óiri; O wa…óta …óum ta∆īe-ta∆īe. A yi'ay to…ďo ngon no yalta hakkude mun. Si O hewtinii ngo e on Mo O muuyi e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, e jaka kam…ďe hi…ďe weltoo"
  30,49,"Gom…óii …ďe laatinoke ado (to…ďo) ngon jippineede e ma…ď…ďe, ko ta∆īinoo…ďe"
  30,50,"Ndaarii e battane yurmeende Alla nden, no O wuurnitorta leydi …ďaawo ndi yoorude. Pellet, wa…óoowo …óum On, ko wuurnitoowo maay…ďe …ďen, Kanko Ko O hattan…óo kala huunde"
  30,51,"[Hay] si Men nulii henndu, …ďe yi'i [gese ma…ď…ďe] …óen no soy…ói, …ďe jokkay …ďaawo …óum, hi…ďe yedda"
  30,52,"Pellet, an a nanintaa maay…ďe …ďen, a nanintaa faa…óu…ďe …ďen kadi noddaandu ndun, si …ďe runtiima …ďe huccinii …ďabbe (ma…ď…ďe)"
  30,53,"A wonaali fewnoowo wum…ďe …ďen e majjere ma…ď…ďe. A nanintaa si wanaa …ďen gom…óim…ďe Aayeeje Amen …óen, hara ko …ďe jebbilii…ďe"